model

Class LatestAddition

  • java.lang.Object
    • model.LatestAddition

  • @Entity(name="LATESTADDITION")
public class LatestAddition
extends java.lang.Object
    Persistant JPA Entity Class

    An entity created in parallel with a FieldValue used to faciliate generating lists of recently added FieldValues

    Has no direct link with its associated FieldValue, but contains information about its name and type to be able to search for the associated FieldValue

    Author:
    Jan Cardenas, Chris Song
